sub_title: Design Engineer | Changing the world one nanometer at a time @ASML
summary:
The ability to describe, predict and above all understand the physical phenomena that are found in nature and by extension our universe has been my main motive for studying and doing research in astronomy and theoretical particle physics. That is also why I am looking for positions where I can keep on using my mathematical, physics and programming skills.    

My other passion is Tang Soo Do, a traditional martial art style from Korea, wherein I have been teaching children and adults.
